IS RECRUIT MORE RESISTANCE.

00:25:30.000 --> 00:25:32.000
TREAT THE PATIENT,
GET HIM WELL,

00:25:32.000 --> 00:25:33.000
THAT'S IT.

00:25:33.000 --> 00:25:37.000
BUT IF YOU USE IT
FOR FIVE TIMES MORE
THAN IT'S NEEDED,

00:25:37.000 --> 00:25:39.000
OR YOU USE IT WHEN
THERE'S A COLD VIRUS

00:25:40.000 --> 00:25:41.000
